1)create a new element (Single, Multiple)
2)append an element inside the parent node
Add the element at the end 
3)InsertBefore(): insert a new node before an existing node on child node of a single parent node
Ex:
<div id="a">
        <h1>Amrutha</h1>
        <h1>Ram</h1>
       </div> 
       <div id="b">
       <h2>sam</h2>
        <h2>venkat</h2>
       </div>
        <script>
            let n = document.createElement("h2")
            n.textContent="Rahul"
            let p = document.getElementById('a')
            let i = document.getElementById('i')
            p.insertBefore(n,i)
            console.log(p)
        </script>
Output:
Amrutha
Ram
Rahul
sam
venkat
