<div id="a">
                <h1>Ravi</h1>
                <h1 id ="r">Ram</h1>
               </div> 
               <div id="b">
               <h2>sam</h2>
                <h2>venkat</h2>
               </div>
                <script>
                    let p=document.createElement("h1")
                    p.innerText="Version"
                    let n=document.getElementById("a")
                    //replace all the element with thr 
                    p.replaceChildren(a)
                    console.log(p)
                    </script>
Output:
